Current Update on Ebola Outbreak
---------------------------------
Cumulative cases: 34 (16 confirmed, 18 probable)
Reported outside Mubende: 3 in Kyegegwa and 1 in Kassanda.
No confirmed cases in Kampala as yet.
Cumulative deaths: 21 (4 confirmed, 17 probable)

--
Communicated by:
Mary Marshall
<mjm2020@googlemail.com>

[The case numbers are rising as expected since the initial patient in whom the disease was identified had not been immediately diagnosed, thereby exposing others to the virus. With recognition of Ebola as the etiologic agent, better precautions against virus transmission will be taken and along with contact tracing, virus spread may be curtailed. - Mod.LK]

